content.text: Now let me compute the ratio based on the claim and the hint formula:

input.command:
sqlite3 "/Users/david/workspace/claude-code-claimdb/test_dbs/california_schools.sqlite" "
SELECT 
  SUM(CASE WHEN FundingType = 'Locally funded' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as locally_funded,
  SUM(CASE WHEN FundingType != 'Locally funded' AND FundingType IS NOT NULL AND FundingType != '' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as other_types,
  COUNT(*) as total_charter,
  ROUND(CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN FundingType = 'Locally funded' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS REAL) / 
    SUM(CASE WHEN FundingType != 'Locally funded' AND FundingType IS NOT NULL AND FundingType != '' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) * 100, 2) as ratio_to_other,
  ROUND(CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN FundingType = 'Locally funded' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS REAL) / 
    SUM(CASE WHEN FundingType IS NOT NULL AND FundingType != '' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) * 100, 2) as ratio_to_all_with_type
FROM schools 
WHERE County = 'Santa Clara' AND Charter = 1;"
